title: Juaari
subTitle: The struggle against a dangerous gambling lord tests Dharam Singh and Vijay as they navigate crime, deception and violence to protect the innocent and reclaim what was lost.

title: Anushka
subTitle: A couple's peaceful night together is shattered by strange and terrifying supernatural events. They must confront the malevolent spirits haunting them to survive the night.

title: Antim Nyay

subTitle: Lal Singh, a righteous and helpful man, clashes against Dayal Singh, a powerful personality. However, things get complicated when a hidden treasure is involved and Lal's tragic past is disclosed.

subTitle: Though Inspector Dayashanker is lazy, he unwittingly unearths a criminal conspiracy and becomes the pride of his division overnight. However, a local gangsters turn his life into a nightmare.

title: Falak
subTitle: Fueled by a deep desire for revenge, two young boys mature into strong-minded adults and set out to secure the justice denied to their father years ago.

title: Face 2 Face
subTitle: An inspector gets suspended for his irascible behaviour. The situation worsens when he gets framed for the murder of an ex-politician's son and must prove his innocence.

subTitle: Nagpal kills Chaudhry and his son, Ram, a military officer. Chaudhry's second son, Vikram, vows to destroy Nagpal who is all set to become the Chief Minister on the upcoming Indian Independence Day.

title: Hindustani Yoddha
subTitle: A young orphan girl suffers at the hands of an evil woman who envies her melodious voice. When she loses hope, her music teacher narrates the story of a heroic man to inspire her.

title: Gurudev

title: Malamaal Company
subTitle: The lives of two flatmates take a dramatic turn when they unexpectedly acquire a parcel containing the country's secrets.

title: Haisiyat

title: Mela
